Invocation Name: swimmerjoe show
des: The SwimmerJoe Show is a nationally syndicated weekly show focusing on competitive swimming, coaching, the Olympics, and the swimmer life. Hosted by Chris Emig and Joe Auer, the show regularly interviews college coaches and Olympians and provides tips and practical advice for coaches, parents, and athletes. Watch live every Sunday at 7 PM EST on the Facebook pages of SwimmerJoe, Florida Swim Network, or Swimming World.
